3. Create the multipart entity: Use the MultipartEntity class to create a multipart entity. Add the image file to the entity using the addPart() method.

4. Set the entity as the content of the request: Use the setEntity() method of the connection object to set the multipart entity as the content of the request.

5. Send the request: Call the connect() method of the connection object to send the request to the server.

